:262px;overflow:hidden">\n<h3>WPM033 2015</h3>\n<p style="margin:5px 0;font-size:16px">Thursday, Oct 29, 2015,  7:00 PM</p>\n<p style="margin: 0 0 5px;"><span style="font-size:14px">Enrise</span><br /><span style="font-size:12px;">Grote Koppel 7 Amersfoort, NL</span></p>\n<p>          <span style="color:#4F8A10;font-size:16px;">26 Developers Went</span>\n<div style="margin:5px 0 10px" class="mu_clearfix">\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/5/e/thumb_247770814.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/7/a/thumb_231510842.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/5/6/3/4/thumb_242122068.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos1.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/8/6/3/4/thumb_242914356.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/6/b/7/thumb_250530391.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/6/a/5/8/thumb_249207224.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos2.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/b/a/4/thumb_234871652.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/4/d/3/9/thumb_246979769.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/a/a/e/6/thumb_250963750.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos4.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/2/8/8/2/thumb_242710370.jpeg" /></div>\n<div class="photo"><img  src="//i2.wp.com/photos3.meetupstatic.com/photos/member/7/8/2/0/thumb_119850752.jpeg" /></div>\n</p></div>\n<p style="line-height:16px">De WordPress Meetup in Amersfoort zal 29 oktober gehouden worden in het pand van Enrise. Enrise zit nabij de oude haven van Amersfoort en is goed bereikbaar met zowel de auto als het openbaar vervoer. Er is plek voor 30